### Get All Posts

GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Get Post By ID
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/6968ce8efd1f1e318c42032b

### Get Posts by Sender
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?sender=You

### Create New Post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "New Sample",
	"content": "Body text",
	"sender": "You"
}

### Update Post
PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/6968ce8efd1f1e318c42032b
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "Updated Sample",
	"content": "Updated Body text",
	"sender": "You"
}

